#X obj 612 679 pack;
#X obj 556 938 bl.tri~;
#X text 66 995 Play some note transitions and then use "create" to
generate the chain or "clear" to forget and erase the memory to start
over. Once you have a chain \, bangs into [markov] start playing the
chain. See [pd MIDI-File] for an example that reads a MIDI File.,
f 52;
